thread.title_full: Vital Choice reviewed by kathy B

author: kathy B
title: kathy B
text:
The process of how the seafood is packaged and shipped is the magic of enjoying seafood cooking at home.
There is no odor when cooking and no odor when reheating! I don't "smell" seafood in my fridge. The taste is fresh and clean even when reheated.
I love the new cod pieces. I usually break up my seafood when cooking to make sure it's thoroughly cooked and now I don't have to.
